social_posts.post_text: ❤️‍🩹I will get up every single time I am pushed down & I hope I can encourage you to do the same! The cancer in my right breast has formed a tumor & is growing rapidly. This Tuesday I have to get a double mastectomy at EMORY😨. I don’t even have time to think about it… Keep Riding, Keep Fighting, & Don’t give up now. ❤️‍🩹🥊 Let’s go! #fighter 🙏🏽

Happy Holidays! Tumor out & 1 step closer. 🥊Get back up & Keep Fighting! 
ILYSM 🖤
#BreastCancer
#DoubleMasectomy
3 years ago doctors told me I would only live for 6 months… I’ll be here forever. 🖤🤍

If you’re close with our family, sorry you’re finding this out on IG, talking about it is emotionally draining and we had to collect ourselves to make this video with smiles. It was perfect timing that Linz was nominated for this awesome opportunity. Please take some time to vote for her for TONY HAWK SKATEPARK HERO! SHE DESERVES IT. Love you all so much. @lindzeyschaffer @tonyhawk

Every day of living with mBC is different. How can you do your best to keep fighting? How can you prepare for the unexpected? 
 
No two stories are the same, and I’ve partnered with @StoryHalfTold to tell mine. Read part one of my blog post at the link in my bio. 
#mBC #StoryHalfTold #Pfizersponsored #ad
Happy to be here surrounded by people i love. 🖤🤎🤍
WHAT. Schāf Window on 34th ST in NYC. Across from the Empire State Building! Walking past this was a dream. My sister @lorenrosko & I are so thankful. Stayed tuned for what’s next 🥹🩷

Saturday, 8/5, I became a FIANCÉ to the love of my life. I couldn’t have dreamed of a more perfect life with a more perfect person. This was the easiest YES ever, ugly sobs and all. I love you with my whole heart, for my whole life.

Zumiez, we love you.🧡 We cried seeing everyone wearing our brand @schafapparel . The secret is, it was our dad’s birthday and he would have been SO proud of us. 👼🏽 Seeing Schaf on so many people from around the country was amazing. #zumiez #zumiezlife #zumiezdrip #zumiezfamily

11Alive Special 💕💪🏼 The truth is, I am not Lindzey’s main support system, I’m just the one who get’s the credit cuz I have the social platform to help share her story. Her ROCK is her fiancé @taylordriggers who is there for the hardest moments. My mom and sister, @_lisahakim_ also do so much more for Linz than I do. It’s all of us. Friends, family, our ATL community and our social media besties! I’m so proud of you @lindzeyschaffer 💕 #KEEPFIGHTING #BreastCancerAwareness

It’s a Christmas miracle 🥹 😍 ⭐️
No #chemotherapy until January.
